title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-04-2014 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-04-2014 TUES


The Glenn Beck Program


          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/4/14Tuesday, March 04, 2014 11:16 AM



Glenn weighs in on the situation in Ukraine 
    and how the president is fumbling the ball on his dealings with Russia.
     
  Also, Professor Ron Rychlak joins the show to discuss his book,
     Disinformation, 
       which he co-authored with an ex-KGB agent, 
         and what to expect from Russia in the ongoing crisis in Crimea.

  Plus, former Senator Jim Demint is on the show to discuss his latest book,
      Falling in Love With America.
